  <title>1: Menu bar and General Toolbars-MD17</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>General Menus and Toolbars</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">1: Menu bar and General Toolbars</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Menu-bar with Commands, or Toolbars, or Both.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You can choose to show only Menu-Bar with commands, only Toolbars, or you can show the Menu-Bar and Toolbars.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2"><image src="1r.gif" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image> Menu bar</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2"><image src="MD-17-Menubar.ipp" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The commands in the <text styleclass="T_Menu">File, Edit, Filters, View, Internet, and Help </text>menus are common to most CAD applications.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The commands in the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Add" styleclass="T_Menu">Function-Blocks, Elements, Sketch, Solids, Visibility, Run, and Dynamics</link><text styleclass="T_Menu">&#32;</text>are those that you use to build your <text styleclass="VariableName">MechDesigner</text> model.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">General toolbars</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="VariableName">General toolbars</text> are <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">above</text> and <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">below</text> the graphics-area. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">All <text styleclass="VariableName">toolbars</text> are collapsed when you start <text styleclass="VariableName">MechDesigner</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">Click the icon to <text styleclass="VariableName">expand </text>and<text styleclass="VariableName"> collapse</text> each <text styleclass="VariableName">toolbar</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">General toolbars <text style="color:#ff0000;">ABOVE</text> the graphics-area</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="MD-TOOLBARS-GENERAL-COLLAPSED-TOP.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><title>General toolbars above graphic-area</title><imagemap><area shape="rect" coords="2,1,42,167" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-File"/><area shape="rect" coords="2,167,366,186" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-File"/><area shape="rect" coords="51,1,91,147" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Solids"/><area shape="rect" coords="51,147,366,166" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Solids"/><area shape="rect" coords="100,1,140,127" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Run"/><area shape="rect" coords="100,127,366,146" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Run"/><area shape="rect" coords="149,1,189,107" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Kinematics"/><area shape="rect" coords="149,107,366,126" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Kinematics"/><area shape="rect" coords="198,1,238,87" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Visibility"/><area shape="rect" coords="198,87,366,106" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Visibility"/><area shape="rect" coords="247,1,287,67" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Edit"/><area shape="rect" coords="247,67,367,86" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Edit"/></imagemap></image></para>
